|4 |│     └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t1      |3       |17          |
|5 |└─PX COORDINATOR           |        |3       |21          |
|6 |  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX20000|3       |20          |
|7 |    └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |3       |17          |
|8 |      └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t2      |3       |17          |
===============================================================
